Marcus Bussey:
 
“Grace-hacks: An event or set of events that will rupture the given
and insert a new expansive awareness into the fabric of our being
 
Grace hacks can be engineered through a wide set of physical
experiences such as play, dance, sex, meditation, collective action
and, of course, drugs (caffeine, through alcohol to heroin). I think of
such experiential processes as grace-hacks.”
(email, May 2020)
 
